         <section id="summary">eqn_block is for a block-level equation. The equation (and possibly the equation identifier, such as a number) is the only content in the block.</section>
      </refbodydiv>
        <refbodydiv outputclass="d4p">
         <section id="d4p">eqn_block is a specialization of p. It can contain MathML.</section>
      </refbodydiv>    	    
