      </refbodydiv>
      <example id="example1">
        <fig><title>Sample of an instance of the eqn_block element</title>
          <codeblock>&lt;p&gt;The following equation is an example of arithmetic.&lt;/p&gt;
          &lt;eqn_block&gt;2 + 2 = 4&lt;/eqn_block&gt;</codeblock></fig>
